{"tid":1058120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"掉出碗公奶！ㄚ頭透膚衣難掩美乳　粉絲驚：太辣了","createTime":"2019-03-12T10:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T10:40:20.000Z","uid":147522,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8635de0ec7a3b235be9ef33f87896994f528582a","tid":1058120,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T10:24:29.000Z","msg":"30歲的丫頭（詹子晴）從《我愛黑澀會》出道，娃娃音、甜美的臉蛋讓外界印象深刻，但她IG一張照片竟意外掉出碗公奶，性感十足，讓人很難想像這是ㄚ頭，還有粉絲驚呼「這也太辣了。」<br />\n<br />\nㄚ頭今天在IG貼出一張照片，問大家「要離開熱帶國家了，台灣天氣還好嗎？」展現難得的性感。照片中的她穿上短版上衣，露出小蠻腰，透膚上衣難擋豐滿上圍，讓ㄚ頭的碗公奶意外現身。<br />\n<br />\n她這照片讓網友驚呼「這也太辣了吧」、「丫頭女神身材好性感」、「流鼻血了。」<br />\n<br />\nㄚ頭今年1月一張照片也讓網友驚呼「長大」，當時她穿低胸、全黑落地褲裝，露出爆乳及深邃事業線，臉上沒有太多表情，看起來氣勢十足。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0762Jv7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0762Jv7.png&h=f7c4056e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea9feff6c836574c0fc52a365036978920e7de1a","tid":1058120,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T10:25:43.000Z","msg":"今次唔使暴動？"},{"pid":"c1f837044f5c54fa3140a1ab9e61059adb84f1ec","tid":1058120,"uid":240613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T10:29:14.000Z","msg":"呢條女把閪聲煩過西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n法官大人都唔屌啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648f54ce7dffa0ea17a5661dce795d0b5ed09fb2","tid":1058120,"uid":234089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T10:29:39.000Z","msg":"邊到辣？"},{"pid":"1ff18bb47e9772d5ee39c0aeefe18480f5f05d21","tid":1058120,"uid":76879,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T10:31:30.000Z","msg":"開開心心屌你老母"},{"pid":"5684184634ce69f3297ba76176a738485b435968","tid":1058120,"uid":167536,"like